{"tid":882095,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"渣打再傳第4季裁員　外媒﹕CFO要求高層「交人頭」及削開支","createTime":"2018-10-30T02:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T12:19:12.000Z","uid":199637,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f605c5be4e5e63fac00104b3067bcc66a31a5a46","tid":882095,"uid":199637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:41:20.000Z","msg":"將於本周三公布第三季業績的渣打集團（2888），再傳出將於第4季進行新一輪裁員行動，《路透》旗下IFR引述渣打財務董事賀方德（Andy Halford）發給公司高層的電郵，要求高層提交削減開支、裁員及投資的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n電郵指出，5月時集團調整削減成本基礎預算，惟至今幾乎全無進展，而收入減慢的情況可能持續到第4季。<br />\n<br />\n早前已有報道，指出渣打擬在中東及非洲裁減300名員工。渣打發言人回應時表示，集團早前公布下半年的開支和上半年差不多，目前仍維持此觀點，集團會於10月31日的第3季業績公布時作出確認。"},{"pid":"a0bea0b16351f7b78fb36b7494e17ab5c5aac823","tid":882095,"uid":199637,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:42:58.000Z","msg":"it狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67fa892d463fc0639c783f886d1e24e9b974fa1","tid":882095,"uid":119979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:44:21.000Z","msg":"DB會點呢唔知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea77b879a19bceb93f3030fa2c552600b8dbd68","tid":882095,"uid":191633,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:54:08.000Z","msg":"人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同我交晒班it狗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488fa01c837c2006cb9080630d10dbed4e89a6e4","tid":882095,"uid":55386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dea77b879a19bceb93f3030fa2c552600b8dbd68","tid":882095,"uid":191633,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:54:08.000Z","msg":"人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同我交晒班it狗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"